{"tid":1114453,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Pioneer車機 藍牙問題","createTime":"2019-04-18T12:43:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T10:20:03.000Z","uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"959b0e6c4352cea792551ce0f2e7edb7748b6f16","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T12:43:32.000Z","msg":"買咗部二手車，部車機係pioneer avh295bt<br />\n<br />\n其他功能冇問題, 唯獨是個藍牙memory full<br />\n<br />\n然後手機就連唔到落去車機<br />\n<br />\n藍牙個選項亦都灰咗， 所以clear唔到memory<br />\n<br />\n睇咗好耐youtube， 話應該係個parking brake冇連到， 解決辦法係一係連番落parking brake一係就ground 咗佢 (eg 將條綠色線駁落機身) <br />\n<br />\n 咁我就諗住自己拆開嚟睇下, 我條綠色線冇啲片入面條parking brake線咁長， 但我都 將條綠色線, 駁落機身試下，但都完全冇用<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cX_5uXKNZ1c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcX_5uXKNZ1c&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=48a8fe99\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cX_5uXKNZ1c</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6S1zkgv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6S1zkgv.jpg&h=5ad11b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇師兄識點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c54d232f05e5087c2e4dc2b29c687da39675e25","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b083cb63c8d461825dd8449b6244793d841367e5","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T13:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6928b4192742b44fa05c5c2d40d1d99962accf61","tid":1114453,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T18:33:27.000Z","msg":"試下用我方法<br />\n得唔得都回一回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n著車之後係車機按關機，再按開機<br />\n您應該會發現原本灰左既藍牙制<br />\n您會入到去，再試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63cb8b1217f6dc2c41385b5d5707bcb9d8e09e41","tid":1114453,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T23:41:20.000Z","msg":"係咪要 Source off 先"},{"pid":"cb10f94cb1b8267a3cb246bfaa87b16aa02698db","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6928b4192742b44fa05c5c2d40d1d99962accf61","tid":1114453,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T18:33:27.000Z","msg":"試下用我方法<br />\n得唔得都回一回我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n著車之後係車機按關機，再按開機<br />\n您應該會發現原本灰左既藍牙制<br />\n您會入到去，再試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T00:59:53.000Z","msg":"部機好似無turn off制，只有off display/sound<br />\n<br />\n但兩樣turn off完再開，個bluetooth制都係仲<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywmfTgf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywmfTgf.jpg&h=46e5d0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n灰左"},{"pid":"548bc0ec9470af5def17393facaa9a76638cdafc","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"63cb8b1217f6dc2c41385b5d5707bcb9d8e09e41","tid":1114453,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T23:41:20.000Z","msg":"係咪要 Source off 先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T01:00:21.000Z","msg":"試過都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1uhm9K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1uhm9K.jpg&h=ab041545&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9519edc32a7b0cd5b100f617391a1cf618ddf20","tid":1114453,"uid":44474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"鬆電池頭，部機就會clear memory"},{"pid":"e4f02473dfd6a7a4e240a559e7c61fe9f0806019","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,