ing brake switch work?<br />\n<br />\nFirst, notice that there is only one wire coming out of the switch. Where's the ground wire? Well, the switch is grounded directly to the chassis of the car so there is no need for a ground wire.<br />\n<br />\nWhen the hand brake is down, it pushes on a little black pin that completes the circuit, grounding the red/black wire.<br />\n<br />\nIn other words, when the hand brake is down, the red/black wire is at 0V, when it's up, the red/black wire is at 12V."},{"pid":"c177bc833a27399edce680e64b3bef731c01c2cb","tid":1114453,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"reset 部機？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJrSX7q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJrSX7q.png&h=21bede31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vRLDTF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvRLDTF8.png&h=4bff4264&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c9e2a27e1f236e4d9afabf9f6c98b5fcf525ef78","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f6b1672124c4bf994d2950c0835356812ff67c6","tid":1114453,"uid":72751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"有無諗過問返賣車果個人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"有問，無回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158ce58abd18c450a7237e48d754698a9da25a97","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fab11703a5466011c81c2b14b0b0e53cca53183","tid":1114453,"uid":18808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ca3caf135d973417265eaa0179517817fcb80d6","tid":1114453,"uid":18808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ba76f80e64a215c2c53a1eb90851cbde1f6cd78","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T01:45:20.000Z","msg":"試過，但係bt個制都係灰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:07:51.000Z","msg":"咁即係條綠線要有12v 先會知你拉起手掣<br />\n諗吓有無計feed 12v 畀佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mechanics.stackexchange.com/questions/53907/pioneer-stereo-parking-brake-wire-issue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmechanics.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F53907%2Fpioneer-stereo-parking-brake-wire-issue&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=5c2d3d1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mechanics.stackexchange.com/questions/53907/pioneer-stereo-parking-brake-wire-issue</a><br />\n<br />\nHow does the parking brake switch work?<br />\n<br />\nFirst, notice that there is only one wire coming out of the switch. Where's the ground wire? Well, the switch is grounded directly to the chassis of the car so there is no need for a ground wire.<br />\n<br />\nWhen the hand brake is down, it pushes on a little black pin that completes the circuit, grounding the red/black wire.<br />\n<br />\nIn other words, when the hand brake is down, the red/black wire is at 0V, when it's up, the red/black wire is at 12V."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"睇唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪將條綠色線駁落去12V 電線？"},{"pid":"44fb85e4a901d8567d888023129a8695d783517b","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c177bc833a27399edce680e64b3bef731c01c2cb","tid":1114453,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"reset 部機？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJrSX7q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJrSX7q.png&h=21bede31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vRLDTF8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvRLDTF8.png&h=4bff4264&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:16:42.000Z","msg":"Method 1,3都試過<br />\nMethod 2 個選項都係灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79cdab843bab2960102e65edc3a2f8986c10f5c3","tid":1114453,"uid":18808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"158ce58abd18c450a7237e48d754698a9da25a97","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fab11703a5466011c81c2b14b0b0e53cca53183","tid":1114453,"uid":18808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ca3caf135d973417265eaa0179517817fcb80d6","tid":1114453,"uid":18808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:07:51.000Z","msg":"咁即係條綠線要有12v 先會知你拉起手掣<br />\n諗吓有無計feed 12v 畀佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mechanics.stackexchange.com/questions/53907/pioneer-stereo-parking-brake-wire-issue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmechanics.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F53907%2Fpioneer-stereo-parking-brake-wire-issue&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=5c2d3d1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mechanics.stackexchange.com/questions/53907/pioneer-stereo-parking-brake-wire-issue</a><br />\n<br />\nHow does the parking brake switch work?<br />\n<br />\nFirst, notice that there is only one wire coming out of the switch. Where's the ground wire? Well, the switch is grounded directly to the chassis of the car so there is no need for a ground wire.<br />\n<br />\nWhen the hand brake is down, it pushes on a little black pin that completes the circuit, grounding the red/black wire.<br />\n<br />\nIn other words, when the hand brake is down, the red/black wire is at 0V, when it's up, the red/black wire is at 12V."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"睇唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪將條綠色線駁落去12V 電線？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"佢話<br />\n<br />\n如果拉起手掣，handbrake switch 會open，你本來應該駁綠色線嗰個位就會有12V<br />\n<br />\n如果鬆手掣，handbrake switch 就會close，將本應接綠線個位ground 左，即係0V<br />\n<br />\n所以我估<br />\n<br />\n綠線sense 到12V 就係拉起手掣，可以unlock 停車的function。0V 就係鬆，會lock 起某啲function。<br />\n<br />\n你試咗將綠線接車殼(ground)，部機都係灰咗。即係後半估啱咗。<br />\n<br />\n然後我再估<br />\n<br />\n會唔會你餵個12V 畀綠線就可以呃倒部機... <br />\n<br />\n明未？"},{"pid":"98d57212662d303dd69cc5f1dbc7f497d4ec1566","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79cdab843bab2960102e65edc3a2f8986c10f5c3","tid":1114453,"uid":18808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"158ce58abd18c450a7237e48d754698a9da25a97","tid":1114453,"uid":137220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fab11703a5466011c81c2b14b0b0e53cca53183","tid":1114453,"uid":18808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mechanics.stackexchange.com/questions/53907/pioneer-stereo-parking-brake-wire-issue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmechanics.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F53907%2Fpioneer-stereo-parking-brake-wire-issue&d=kjYWGV%2FOxf%2BJAuwkXUN1dLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=5c2d3d1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mechanics.stackexchange.com/questions/53907/pioneer-stereo-parking-brake-wire-issue</a><br />\n<br />\nHow does the parking brake switch work?<br />\n<br />\nFirst, notice that there is only one wire coming out of the switch. Where's the ground wire? Well, the switch is grounded directly to the chassis of the car so there is no need for a ground wire.<br />\n<br />\nWhen the hand brake is down, it pushes on a little black pin that completes the circuit, grounding the red/black wire.<br />\n<br />\nIn other words, when the hand brake is down, the red/black wire is at 0V, when it's up, the red/black wire is at 12V."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T10:15:45.000Z","msg":"睇唔太明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪將條綠色線駁落去12V 電線？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T01:34:31.000Z","msg":"佢話<br />\n<br />\n如果拉起手掣，handbrake switch 會open，你本來應該駁綠色線嗰個位就會有12V<br />\n<br />\n如果鬆手掣，handbrake switch 就會close，將本應接綠線個位ground 左，即係0V<br />\n<br />\n所以我估<br />\n<br />\n綠線sense 到12V 就係拉起手掣，可以unlock 停車的function。0V 就係鬆，會lock 起某啲function。<br />\n<br />\n你試咗將綠線接車殼(ground)，部機都係灰咗。即係後半估啱咗。<br />\n<br />\n然後我再估<br />\n<br />\n會唔會你餵個12V 畀綠線就可以呃倒部機... <br />\n<br />\n明未？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FQoRAVc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFQoRAVc.jpg&h=6c9982cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n紅線係12v， 我將綠線駁埋落去啱唔啱？<br />\n<br />\n咁樣搏完都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}